arts.ttl: LEAKED: Adidas Creates Custom "SGE Red" for Eintracht Frankfurt Kits - No More Nike
arts.sum: Adidas will replace Nike as Eintracht Frankfurt kit maker for the 2025-26 season and beyond.

arts.ttl: Omar Marmoush: Frankfurt chief issues major Man City transfer update as £67m forward scores in Bundesliga win
arts.sum: Eintracht Frankfurt chief Markus Krosche delivers an update on the future of Man City-linked Omar Marmoush, who scored in the Bundesliga club's 1-0 win over St Pauli on Saturday.

arts.ttl: Reported Man City target Marmoush scores again for Frankfurt in Bundesliga
arts.sum: Reported Manchester City target Omar Marmoush boosted his transfer value with another goal for Eintracht Frankfurt to beat St. Pauli 1-0 in the Bundesliga on Saturday. Marmoush has 19 goals in 25 games across all competitions for Frankfurt this season.

arts.ttl: Omar Marmoush's strike helps Eintracht Frankfurt down St. Pauli
arts.sum: Eintracht Frankfurt secured a narrow 1-0 victory over St. Pauli on Matchday 16, with Omar Marmoush's first-half goal the difference between the two sides at the Millerntor Stadion. Omar Marmoush celebrates his match-winning goal, showcasing his importance to Frankfurt's success - IMAGO/Justus Stegemann

arts.ttl: Man City 'closing in' on Omar Marmoush transfer: When could Eintracht Frankfurt star join Pep Guardiola's side?
arts.sum: Manchester City are reportedly closing in on a deal to make Eintracht Frankfurt forward Omar Marmoush their second addition of the winter transfer window.

arts.ttl: Official Manchester City bid for Omar Marmoush expected this weekend
arts.sum: An official bid from Manchester City for Eintracht Frankfurt forward Omar Marmoush is expected this weekend, according to Florian Plettenburg. The Egyptian international has been high on City’s wish list…

arts.ttl: Frankfurt line up Rennes striker as replacement for Manchester City target Marmoush
arts.sum: Sky Sport Germany transfer specialist Florian Plettenberg has today reported that Eintracht Frankfurt are looking at Rennes forward Arnaud Kalimuendo (23) as a candidate to replace Omar Marmoush, should the Egyptian…

arts.ttl: Man City transfer news: Pep Guardiola makes stance on new signings crystal clear amid Omar Marmoush, Abdukodir Khusanov, Vitor Reis links
arts.sum: Manchester City manager Pep Guardiola makes his feelings "clear" over potential incomings and outgoings at the Etihad Stadium during the January transfer window.

arts.ttl: Spurs transfer news: Forward being lined up as Omar Marmoush replacement at Eintracht Frankfurt?
arts.sum: Eintracht Frankfurt are allegedly lining up a struggling Tottenham Hotspur attacker as a potential replacement for Omar Marmoush.

arts.ttl: Pep Guardiola responds to Omar Marmoush claim with Man City transfer update
arts.sum: Reports in Germany suggest that Eintracht Frankfurt star Omar Marmoush has agreed personal terms with Man City
